#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn15.8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn15.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 15 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 15 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. The First Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn15.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Gaṅgāsutta "
msgstr "8. The Ganges "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn15.8:1.1"
msgid "Rājagahe viharati veḷuvane. "
msgstr "Near Rājagaha, in the Bamboo Grove. "

msgctxt "sn15.8:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. "
msgstr "Then a certain brahmin went up to the Buddha, and exchanged greetings with him. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.8:1.3"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one side and asked the Buddha, "

msgctxt "sn15.8:1.4"
msgid "“kīvabahukā nu kho, bho gotama, kappā abbhatītā atikkantā”ti? "
msgstr "“Sir, how many eons have passed?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.8:1.5"
msgid "“Bahukā kho, brāhmaṇa, kappā abbhatītā atikkantā. "
msgstr "“Brahmin, many eons have passed. "

msgctxt "sn15.8:1.6"
msgid "Te na sukarā saṅkhātuṃ: "
msgstr "It’s not easy to calculate "

msgctxt "sn15.8:1.7"
msgid "‘ettakā kappā iti vā, ettakāni kappasatāni iti vā, ettakāni kappasahassāni iti vā, ettakāni kappasatasahassāni iti vā’”ti. "
msgstr "how many eons have passed, how many hundreds or thousands or hundreds of thousands of eons.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.184, sc2
msgctxt "sn15.8:2.1"
msgid "“Sakkā pana, bho gotama, upamaṃ kātun”ti? "
msgstr "“But sir, can you give a simile?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.8:2.2"
msgid "“Sakkā, brāhmaṇā”ti bhagavā avoca. "
msgstr "“I can,” said the Buddha. "

# NOTE: BB’s translation here appears ill-formed.
#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.8:2.3"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, brāhmaṇa, yato cāyaṃ gaṅgā nadī pabhavati yattha ca mahāsamuddaṃ appeti, yā etasmiṃ antare vālikā sā na sukarā saṅkhātuṃ: "
msgstr "“Consider the Ganges river from where it originates to where it enters the ocean. Between these places it’s not easy to calculate "

msgctxt "sn15.8:2.4"
msgid "‘ettakā vālikā iti vā, ettakāni vālikasatāni iti vā, ettakāni vālikasahassāni iti vā, ettakāni vālikasatasahassāni iti vā’ti. "
msgstr "how many grains of sand there are, how many hundreds or thousands or hundreds of thousands of grains of sand. "

msgctxt "sn15.8:2.5"
msgid "Tato bahutarā kho, brāhmaṇa, kappā abbhatītā atikkantā. "
msgstr "The eons that have passed are more than this. "

msgctxt "sn15.8:2.6"
msgid "Te na sukarā saṅkhātuṃ: "
msgstr "It’s not easy to calculate "

msgctxt "sn15.8:2.7"
msgid "‘ettakā kappā iti vā, ettakāni kappasatāni iti vā, ettakāni kappasahassāni iti vā, ettakāni kappasatasahassāni iti vā’ti. "
msgstr "how many eons have passed, how many hundreds or thousands or hundreds of thousands of eons. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.8:2.8"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "sn15.8:2.9"
msgid "Anamataggoyaṃ, brāhmaṇa, saṃsāro. "
msgstr "Transmigration has no known beginning. "

msgctxt "sn15.8:2.10"
msgid "Pubbā koṭi na paññāyati avijjānīvaraṇānaṃ sattānaṃ taṇhāsaṃyojanānaṃ sandhāvataṃ saṃsarataṃ. "
msgstr "No first point is found of sentient beings roaming and transmigrating, hindered by ignorance and fettered by craving. "

msgctxt "sn15.8:2.11"
msgid "Evaṃ dīgharattaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, dukkhaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ tibbaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ byasanaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ, kaṭasī vaḍḍhitā. "
msgstr "For such a long time you have undergone suffering, agony, and disaster, swelling the cemeteries. "

msgctxt "sn15.8:2.12"
msgid "Yāvañcidaṃ, brāhmaṇa, alameva sabbasaṅkhāresu nibbindituṃ, alaṃ virajjituṃ, alaṃ vimuccitun”ti. "
msgstr "This is quite enough for you to become disillusioned, dispassionate, and freed regarding all conditions.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn15.8:3.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, so brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When he said this, the brahmin said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "sn15.8:3.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe … "
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent! … "

msgctxt "sn15.8:3.3"
msgid "upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti. "
msgstr "From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn15.8:3.4"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

